description._content: Description: His Excellency and Mr. J.M. Pattinson escorting Sir Bernard Reilly into the luncheon tent. Location: Aden, Yemen Date: 03 February 1953 Description: Light refreshments. His Excellency and Mr. Pattinson. Location: Aden, Yemen Date: 03 February 1953 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/684 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
